          "html": "<style>\n  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&display=swap');\n  :root {\n    --color-notebook-paper: #fffef6;\n    --color-ink-black: #000000;\n    --color-pure-white: #ffffff;\n    --color-blush-pink: #f8c8d8;\n    --color-sunrise-yellow: #fdcf85;\n    --font-margo-pro: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;\n    --shadow-subtle: rgb(0,0,0) 2px 2px 0px 0px;\n  }\n  .mission-wrapper {\n    background: var(--color-notebook-paper);\n    background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(transparent, transparent 27px, rgba(0,0,0,0.06) 27px, rgba(0,0,0,0.06) 28px), repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, transparent 27px, rgba(0,0,0,0.04) 27px, rgba(0,0,0,0.04) 28px);\n    padding: 44px 32px;\n    font-family: var(--font-margo-pro);\n    border: 1px solid var(--color-ink-black);\n  }\n  .mission-headline {\n    font-family: var(--font-margo-pro);\n    font-size: 32px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    color: var(--color-ink-black);\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    line-height: 1.1;\n    letter-spacing: normal;\n    margin: 0 0 24px 0;\n    max-width: 480px;\n  }\n  .mission-body {\n    font-family: var(--font-margo-pro);\n    font-size: 16px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    color: var(--color-ink-black);\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    line-height: 1.3;\n    letter-spacing: normal;\n    margin: 0 0 32px 0;\n    max-width: 440px;\n    opacity: 0.75;\n  }\n  .mission-cta-row {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 16px;\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n  }\n  .mission-link {\n    font-family: var(--font-margo-pro);\n    font-size: 16px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    color: var(--color-ink-black);\n    text-decoration: none;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    display: inline-flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 8px;\n    position: relative;\n  }\n  .mission-link::after {\n    content: '';\n    position: absolute;\n    bottom: -4px;\n    left: 0;\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 2px;\n    background: var(--color-blush-pink);\n  }\n  .stamp {\n    display: inline-flex;\n    flex-direction: column;\n    align-items: center;\n    justify-content: center;\n    width: 72px;\n    height: 72px;\n    border: 2px solid var(--color-ink-black);\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background: var(--color-notebook-paper);\n    position: relative;\n    margin-left: auto;\n  }\n  .stamp::before {\n    content: '';\n    position: absolute;\n    inset: 3px;\n    border: 1.5px dashed var(--color-ink-black);\n    border-radius: 50%;\n  }\n  .stamp-text {\n    font-family: var(--font-margo-pro);\n    font-size: 9px;\n    color: var(--color-ink-black);\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    text-align: center;\n    line-height: 1.1;\n    position: relative;\n    z-index: 1;\n  }\n  .stats-row {\n    display: flex;\n    gap: 0;\n    margin-top: 32px;\n    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-ink-black);\n  }\n  .stat-item {\n    flex: 1;\n    padding: 16px 8px 8px 8px;\n    border-right: 1px solid var(--color-ink-black);\n  }\n  .stat-item:last-child {\n    border-right: none;\n  }\n  .stat-number {\n    font-family: var(--font-margo-pro);\n    font-size: 32px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    color: var(--color-ink-black);\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    line-height: 1.0;\n    display: block;\n  }\n  .stat-label {\n    font-family: var(--font-margo-pro);\n    font-size: 12px;\n    font-weight: 400;\n    color: var(--color-ink-black);\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n    display: block;\n    opacity: 0.6;\n    margin-top: 4px;\n  }\n  .badge-inline {\n    font-family: var(--font-margo-pro);\n    font-size: 12px;\n    background: var(--color-sunrise-yellow);\n    color: var(--color-ink-black);\n    padding: 1.6px 8px;\n    border-radius: 0px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    display: inline-block;\n  }\n</style>\n<div class='mission-wrapper'>\n  <div style='display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:8px;'>\n    <span class='badge-inline'>Our Mission</span>\n    <div class='stamp' style='margin-left:auto;margin-top:-8px;'>\n      <span class='stamp-text'>Since<br>2001<br>Oatly</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 class='mission-headline'>We exist to make it easier for people to live healthier lives without recklessly taxing the planet's resources in the process.</h2>\n  <p class='mission-body'>We are a company that believes in both making a difference and making a profit. Because a healthier future for both humans and the planet requires us to stick around.</p>\n  <div class='mission-cta-row'>\n    <a href='#' class='mission-link'>Read More <svg width='16' height='10' viewBox='0 0 16 10' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'><path d='M1 5H15M15 5L11 1M15 5L11 9' stroke='#000' stroke-width='1.5'/></svg></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class='stats-row'>\n    <div class='stat-item'>\n      <span class='stat-number'>70%</span>\n      <span class='stat-label'>Less CO₂ vs. dairy</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class='stat-item'>\n      <span class='stat-number'>79%</span>\n      <span class='stat-label'>Less land use</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class='stat-item'>\n      <span class='stat-number'>60%</span>\n      <span class='stat-label'>Less energy</span>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
